column5: Went fishing Saturday. Some fish were caught, more were lost, it was cold and windy. That is all!!!
Am I a tool for looking at that white box waiting for a picture to appear on my crap-piece computer lol????  Burt ;-)
To the victor go the spoils!!! And in case you were wondering, IT WAS AWESOME!!!!!
You went fishing and caught fish.
Beer batter trout / salad? and green beans. I like you man but stay out of my fish hut.....
Don't be so surprised, it can happen. Even a blind squirrel finds a nut once in a while.    It's slaw not salad.
Yummmmmm, now that looks good!!!  Love the snow picture, looks like a complete blizzard
